<div class=3DWordSection1>

<p class=3DMsoNormal>TAGGING VLAN CISCO NEXUS DAN QinQ<br style=3D'mso-spec=
ial-character:
line-break'>
<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style=3D'mso-special-character:line-bre=
ak'>
<![endif]></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt=
:auto;
line-height:normal'><span style=3D'font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New =
Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Untuk membuat VLAN dan melakukan
tagging pada switch Cisco Nexus, Anda bisa mengikuti langkah-langkah beriku=
t.
Pastikan Anda memiliki akses ke perangkat dan hak istimewa yang diperlukan
untuk melakukan konfigurasi.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt=
:auto;
line-height:normal;mso-outline-level:3'><b><span style=3D'font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roma=
n"'>1.
Masuk ke Mode Konfigurasi<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt=
:auto;
line-height:normal'><span style=3D'font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New =
Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Pertama, masuk ke switch Anda
melalui SSH atau konsol, lalu masuk ke mode konfigurasi.<o:p></o:p></span><=
/p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-=
height:
normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.=
4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt'><span
style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier New";mso-fareast-font-family=
:"Times New Roman"'>enable<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-=
height:
normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.=
4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt'><span
style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier New";mso-fareast-font-family=
:"Times New Roman"'>configure
terminal<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt=
:auto;
line-height:normal;mso-outline-level:3'><b><span style=3D'font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roma=
n"'>2.
Membuat VLAN<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt=
:auto;
line-height:normal'><span style=3D'font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New =
Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Gunakan perintah berikut untuk
membuat VLAN baru. Misalnya, untuk membuat VLAN 10:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-=
height:
normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.=
4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt'><span
style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier New";mso-fareast-font-family=
:"Times New Roman"'>vlan
10<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-=
height:
normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.=
4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt'><span
style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Courier New";mso-fareast-font-family=
:"Times New Roman"'><span
style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>name VLAN10<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt=
:auto;
line-height:normal;mso-outline-level:3'><b><span style=3D'font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roma=
n"'>3.
Mengonfigurasi Interface<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

